| Issue                          | Possible Cause               | Solution                      |
| ------------------------------ | ---------------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| Light not turning ON           | PIR sensor not detecting     | Adjust sensitivity / range    |
| Fan not turning ON             | LM35 not calibrated          | Check wiring, threshold value |
| Relay clicking repeatedly      | Loose power supply           | Tighten connections           |
| PIR false triggers             | Direct sunlight interference | Cover sensor with black tape  |
| Temperature readings incorrect | Wrong formula or pin         | Verify analog pin & scaling   |
